OL,5, When Valeriya, Emad and their two boys 
OL,6, needed refuge from Russian missiles,   
OL,7, the Groves family were only too pleased
OL,8, to provide sanctuary.                  
OL,10,FBut months on from fleeing the war in  
OL,11,FUkraine, the Sloz family wanted to find
OL,12,Fa place in the UK to call their own -  
OL,13,Fbut that is where it got tricky.       
OL,15,FHosts were initially asked to provide  
OL,16,Frefugees a roof for six months but what
OL,17,Fhappens next has left some in limbo.   
OL,19,FThe only way Valeriya's family got a UK
OL,20,Fhome was their hosts being a guarantor.
